Title: Cozy Camouflage
Description:
<Posidriss yawns.>

I just can't sleep. Let's play a game instead!

Maybe there's a comfy hiding spot out there somewhere. I bet you can't find me in the city!
ObjectivesText: Find Posidriss and their friends in Valdrakken.
RewardText:
Thanks, $n! That was really fun!

I just wish I could get to sleep...
